{{> layout/header}}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5" style="max-width:640px;">
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-center text-danger">회원 탈퇴</h2>
    <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">
        <p class="mb-4 text-center">
            탈퇴하시면 모든 정보가 삭제되며 복구할 수 없습니다.<br>
            <strong>이 작업은 되돌릴 수 없습니다.</strong>
        </p>
        <form method="post" action="/view/mypage/withdraw" class="d-grid gap-2">
            <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">회원 탈퇴</button>
            <a href="/view/mypage" class="btn btn-secondary">취소</a>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

{{> layout/footer}}
